movies.title: More Human Than Human
movies.summary: More Human Than Human explores the promises and the complex role of Artificial Intelligence in today's world and the consequences of those promises becoming reality. In this feature length documentary the filmmaker attempts to build an intelligent robot to see if it can replace him as the film director. Will our creation, infinitely smarter, interconnected and possibly self-aware, render humanity obsolete?

movies.title: Froning: The Fittest Man in History
movies.title_english: Froning: The Fittest Man in History
movies.title_long: Froning: The Fittest Man in History (2015)
movies.summary: Rich Froning Jr. is a legend in CrossFit and the Sport of Fitness. In this biopic, take a look at his childhood, follow his quest for a fourth CrossFit Games title, and see him as a son, a husband and a new father.
